summary: The houses on finding a husband for Ravenclaw.
body:
The houses on finding a husband for Ravenclaw.

Hufflepuff: you need to marry a rich man. We all know you won’t marry out of love.

Ravenclaw: yea, okay.

Hufflepuff: and i want half of the money you get.

Ravenclaw: what, no? i worked for that.

Slytherin: okay, wait. we split the money evenly. Huff gets a rich man. i manipulate him into liking you. you marry him and we get the money.

summary: Attraction: The House of Minalima, Greek Street, London Even with the changing displays and additions to the store, artwork from...
caption:
Attraction: The House of Minalima, Greek Street, London

Even with the changing displays and additions to the store, artwork from the Harry Potter Film Series has remain consistent since 2016. One popular draw, on the third floor, is the fireplace of Hogwarts Letters - the perfect photo opportunity - though, you will need to resist trying to steal one of the letters!

Little tip for Fans - If you don’t ever get to visit the House of Minalima, don’t panic! The majority of the items Minalima designed can also be see at WBTour London!

summary: I was trying to hide the Deathly Hallows from Thanos and I was literally in my living room while my parents were telling me that...
body: I was trying to hide the Deathly Hallows from Thanos and I was literally in my living room while my parents were telling me that Thanos was approaching and then they left through the front door. There was one of those Christmas stockings hanging from a nail on the plastic frame part of the window and I took a huge pebble out of my cardigan’s pocket - which represented the Deathly Hallows. Thanos kicked my door off its hinges and entered my living room right as I was putting the Hallows inside the stocking and he was trying to pull me from it, and I was stretching like one of those old cartoons and I finally put the pebble in right before he managed to pull me and throw me from my balcony but I knew my mission was accomplished. I woke up before dying.
